        <source>updateMultiReleases(_cmifBookingRef : CMIF_BookingRef) updating;
/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Created:	19 February 2010	by cnwvu1

Purpose:	
   
Change Date		Who		Reason
13/02/2012		cnwcs5	par 28756 - isBookingRequest property deleted
25/05/2016		cnwma1	PAR #37790 TFS#1880 MSL - EDI Bookings with Release Empties 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
vars

begin

	//if self.checkIfUpdateMultiRelease()  then					// 25/05/2016 cnwma1 PAR #37790 TFS #1880
	if self.checkIfUpdateMultiRelease(_cmifBookingRef)  then	// 25/05/2016 cnwma1 PAR #37790 TFS #1880
